# 🐤 Flappy Bird Clone

A browser-based Flappy Bird remake built with vanilla JavaScript, HTML, and CSS. Dodge pipes, earn points, and test your reflexes in this fast-paced side-scroller — now with high score tracking and adaptive difficulty.

## 🚀 Features

- 🎮 Smooth gameplay using `requestAnimationFrame`
- 🧠 Realistic physics with gravity and jump mechanics
- 🌪️ Increasing difficulty as your score rises
- 🏆 LocalStorage-based high score saving
- 🚨 Visual red warning flash when you're near the ground, ceiling, or pipes
- 🔁 Instant restart on crash
- 🎨 Lightweight, responsive UI

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **HTML/CSS** – Page structure and styling  
- **JavaScript** – Game logic, animation, collision detection, score tracking  
- **LocalStorage API** – Saves high score across browser sessions  

## 🎯 How to Play

- Press **Enter** to start or restart the game  
- Use the **Up Arrow** or **Spacebar** to make the bird fly  
- Avoid hitting the pipes or the edges of the screen  
- Score points by passing through the pipe gaps  
- The game gets harder as your score increases  

